title: Marvel Now! - Week 10/16/2013
description:
Hello everybody! Here the new Marvel NOW! comic pack!
The special mentions of this week go to:

- Avengers 21, Avengers Assemble 20 and New Avengers 11, Tie-Ins of Infinity!
- The last part of the mini-saga Hunger, with Hunger 4
- Indestructible Hulk Special 1, part two of The Arms of Octopus", beginned with All-New X-Men Special 1 of the last week.
- The return of Clint Barton and his comic, Hawkeye 13. I know a lot of you was waiting for it.
- Uncanny X-Men 13, 8th part of "Battle for the Atom".

For this week is all, people.
See ya soon!

PS: I've upped another torrent, but in the wrong category, so i re-upped this in the right one. Sorry for the inconvenience^^
